::Reptilica/DevilDuer::

DeviDuer opens his eyes. He was being carried down a hallway, by a bot who 
smelled like charred trees. "What's goin' on?" he asks dizzily.

Reptilica stops, putting DevilDuer down. "You were knocked out, and starting 
talking strangely, so I'm taking you to a CR chamber."

DevilDuer shakes his head, "No, I'm fine."

Reptilica nods. "Allright then." He turns a corner, heading toward the 
bridge. DevilDuer follows him.
